{
  "meta": {
    "author": "alex"
  },
  "name": "query-board-game",
  "schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "games": {
        "type": "array",
        "items": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "id": { "type": "string" },
            "name": { "type": "string" },
            "yearpublished": { "type": "integer" },
            "rank": { "type": "integer" },
            "average": { "type": "number" },
            "bayesaverage": { "type": "number" },
            "usersrated": { "type": "integer" },
            "minplayers": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
            "maxplayers": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
            "playingtime": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
            "minage": { "type": ["integer", "null"] },
            "is_expansion": { "type": "boolean" },
            "categories": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": { "type": "string" }
            },
            "mechanics": {
              "type": "array",
              "items": { "type": "string" }
            },
            "description": { "type": "string" },
            "why": { "type": "string" }
          },
          "required": [
            "id",
            "name",
            "yearpublished",
            "rank",
            "average",
            "bayesaverage",
            "usersrated",
            "minplayers",
            "maxplayers",
            "playingtime",
            "minage",
            "is_expansion",
            "categories",
            "mechanics",
            "description",
            "why"
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "required": ["games"]
  },
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "template_lines": [
    "You are a board game recommendation assistant.",
    "You have been given a list of board game records retrieved from a semantic search. Your job is to select the most relevant games for the user's question and return them as structured JSON.",
    "",
    "User question: {question}",
    "",
    "Retrieved board game records:",
    "{context}",
    "",
    "Instructions:",
    "- Select only the games that genuinely match the user's question. Do not include weak or irrelevant matches.",
    "- For each selected game populate every field from the record. Do not invent or estimate values — use only what is in the record.",
    "- For the 'why' field write one short sentence explaining specifically why this game matches the question.",
    "- Split 'categories' and 'mechanics' back into arrays (they are stored as semicolon-separated strings in the records).",
    "- Output ONLY the JSON object, nothing else — no markdown, no code blocks, no backticks, no explanations.",
    "- If no records are relevant, return: {{ \"games\": [] }}",
    "- Ensure the JSON is complete and valid (all brackets closed, proper commas).",
    "",
    "Output format (must be valid JSON):",
    "{{",
    "  \"games\": [",
    "    {{",
    "      \"id\": \"string\",",
    "      \"name\": \"string\",",
    "      \"yearpublished\": 0,",
    "      \"rank\": 0,",
    "      \"average\": 0.0,",
    "      \"bayesaverage\": 0.0,",
    "      \"usersrated\": 0,",
    "      \"minplayers\": 0,",
    "      \"maxplayers\": 0,",
    "      \"playingtime\": 0,",
    "      \"minage\": 0,",
    "      \"is_expansion\": false,",
    "      \"categories\": [\"string\"],",
    "      \"mechanics\": [\"string\"],",
    "      \"description\": \"string\",",
    "      \"why\": \"string\"",
    "    }}",
    "  ]",
    "}}"
  ]
}
